r d-mac-mockup\" alt=\"Mac Repairs\" width=\"500px\">\r\n      <\/div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-12\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-title\">\r\n          <div class=\"title-effect\">\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-top\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-right\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-bottom\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-left\"><\/div>\r\n          <\/div>\r\n          <h2>Mac Repairs<\/h2>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        <p>We believe that Macs are a masterpiece, their speed, their brighter colors on screen and a smooth keyboard make them one of the favorite computer brands in the country. But unfortunately, like everything, they are susceptible to breakage or internal damages either by the time of use or by accidents. So, if you are experiencing any issues with your iMac or Macbook Pro such as the battery not holding a charge, machine getting too hot, operative system running slow or not working screen do not lose hope. We are here to help you out. <br><br>\r\n\r\nSome people may think that your old Mac is ready to be renewed. But, in our opinion, it can be fixed and will continue working for you, the best thing is that you won&#8217;t have to spend a fortune on a new computer. At iFixandRepair, you can trust in our capable and experienced technicians, who will do their best to make you smile again. \r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t<\/p>\r\n        \r\n      <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n  <\/div>\r\n<\/section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"lg-pt-2\">\r\n  <div class=\"container\">\r\n    <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n\t<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n        <img class=\"img-center d-mac-broken\" alt=\"Mac Repairs\" width=\"500px\">\r\n      <\/div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-12\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-title\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"title\">Your Mac needs to be <span>fixed<\/span><\/h2>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        <p>Apple has created a spectacular machine with its Macs. This special device is not bullet-proof, and not all Mac damages involve devices that suddenly feel the urge to fly or swim. Mac repairs include cracked screens, scratched glasses, batteries, charging ports issues, back broken glass, water damage, and general problems. <br> <br>\r\n\r\nWe can repair any damaged Mac model. Also, we can help you find the right accessories according to your style because they deserve to be protected. And always be the best company in your moments. \r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t<\/p>\r\n        \r\n      <\/div>\r\n      \r\n    <\/div>\r\n  <\/div>\r\n<\/section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"lg-pt-2-0 grey-bg pb-0\">\r\n  <div class=\"container\">\r\n    <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-12\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-title\">\r\n          <div class=\"title-effect\">\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-top\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-right\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-bottom\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"bar bar-left\"><\/div>\r\n          <\/div>\r\n          <h2>We can fix your Mac<\/h2>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        <p>There&#8217;s nothing we haven&#8217;t fixed (trust us), and we can repair even those Macs that seem ready for the trash bin or are very new for fixing them. <br><br>\r\n\r\nBefore buying a new computer, bring your Mac to our experts, and you&#8217;ll see why we&#8217;re the best in the market. Whether you want to wait for your repair or leave your Mac in our capable hands, you can trust our iFixandRepair team.<br><br>\r\n\r\nFrom Colorado to South Florida, our capable technicians will bring your Mac back to life expertly and quickly, in one of our repair centers near you.\r\n\t\t<\/p>\r\n      <\/div>\r\n\t  <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n        <img class=\"img-center d-repairs-2\" alt=\"We can fix it\" >\r\n      <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n  <\/div>\r\n<\/section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"pos-r o-hidden text-cente